text: The Gunther's triangle frog, Guenther's Triangle Frog or Solomon Island eyelash frog (Cornufer guentheri) is a frog. It lives on all of the Solomon Islands except for one, San Cristobal. Scientists have seen it between 0 and 830 meters above sea level. ==References== Category:Frogs of Oceania
title: Cornufer guentheri
